    <item>
      <title>预计未来五年美国电力需求将增长 16%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/us-electricity-demand-forecast-to-surge-16-over-next-five-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新报告显示，受新建数据中心和工厂大量用电的推动，未来五年美国的电力需求将激增近 16%，是一年前预估的三倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/us-electricity-demand-forecast-to-surge-16-over-next-five-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>重新评估“独角兽”地位的基准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/reevaluating-the-benchmark-of-unicorn-status-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Canvas Ventures 联合创始人兼普通合伙人 Rebecca Lynn 表示，如今“独角兽”地位的基准意义不大，因为人工智能有助于加速收入增长。她与 Caroline Hyde 一起讨论“彭博科技”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/reevaluating-the-benchmark-of-unicorn-status-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总统马克龙称他不会辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/french-president-macron-says-he-s-not-resigning-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，他将完成剩余总统任期，以期迅速平息法国政坛动荡。此前，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党与左翼议员联手推翻了他的政府。他在电视讲话中发表了上述讲话。彭博社记者斯蒂芬·卡罗尔在巴黎报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/french-president-macron-says-he-s-not-resigning-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于安全问题，美国宇航局不得不推迟登月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/nasa-has-to-delay-moon-landing-due-to-safety-issues-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国宇航局不得不将重返月球的任务推迟到 2027 年。猎户座飞船的隔热罩存在严重的安全问题。一项名为 Artemis II 的前身任务也被推迟。布鲁斯·艾因霍恩 (Bruce Einhorn) 提供了所有最新消息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-05/nasa-has-to-delay-moon-landing-due-to-safety-issues-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:39:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞预算言论导致法国债券风险降至两周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/french-bonds-outperform-as-le-pen-revives-hopes-of-budget-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者希望法国议员能比许多投资者预期的更早就明年的预算达成协议，从而结束持续数月令市场承压的政治僵局，衡量法国债券风险的一项指标出现下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/french-bonds-outperform-as-le-pen-revives-hopes-of-budget-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果马克龙放宽债务路径，勒庞将在未来几周内公布法国预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/le-pen-france-budget-likely-within-weeks-if-macron-eases-debt-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞表示，只要下一任总理准备以更慢的速度缩小赤字，法国就能克服政府垮台并在“几周内”出台预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/le-pen-france-budget-likely-within-weeks-if-macron-eases-debt-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 13:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
